article_title: Nursing program ranked top in nation
article_text:
Normal, IL (61790)

Today

A few isolated thunderstorms developing during the afternoon. High 86F. Winds SSW at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 30%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening, then cloudy skies overnight. Low 68F. Winds S at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

og.description: U.S. News and World Report ranked Illinois State University’s online graduate nursing program among the top in the nation for 2015.
